[SN]TITLE[SN]
More Christmas shoppers than ever at risk from fraud say police

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
If you are planning to do some or all of your Christmas shopping online, are you aware of all of the risks?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
29 November 2014 Last updated at 13:32 GMT
A number of agencies including the police have said more Christmas shoppers than ever in Northern Ireland are at risk from fraudulent scams.
BBC Newsline's Kevin Sharkey reports.
